name: Skateboard Decks
description: Custom skateboard decks digitally printed and laminated with the highest quality media by Oracal.  Decks are made of 7 ply maple and wrapped with the digital skin.  Purchase your deck and then email your image to wrapturegraphics@gmail.com  We will then produce a digital mock up for your approval before printing the deck.  Please note the image size is 8 1/2" x 33"  this size includes print bleed.  We accept jpegs, ai, eps or tiff files.  Please make sure to send the highest resolution file available.  These decks are the perfect gift and great to hang on any wall!  You can also shred on them if you'd like. Wholesale prices available, call for details.
